*Licu* je bilo bledo od straha. (His face was pale from fear.)

*Licu* je obasjalo svetlo nade. (A light of hope illuminated his face.)

*Lica* su im se smejala. (Their faces were smiling.)

*Licu* je jecala od bola. (His face was crying from pain.)

*Lica* su bila zbunjena. (Their faces were confused.)